Task 1: Handle JavaScript Simple Alert
1. Go to https://the-internet.herokuapp.com/.
2. Click "JavaScript Alerts".
3. Click "Click for JS Alert" and accept the alert.

Task 2: Handle JavaScript Confirm Alert
1. Go to https://the-internet.herokuapp.com/.
2. Click "JavaScript Alerts".
3. Click "Click for JS Confirm" and dismiss the alert.

Task 3: Handle JavaScript Prompt Alert
1. Go to https://the-internet.herokuapp.com/.
2. Click "JavaScript Alerts".
3. Click "Click for JS Prompt".
4. Enter "Hello, Selenium" and accept the alert.
5. Print the result.

Task 4: Handle Alert on Right Click
1. Go to https://the-internet.herokuapp.com/context_menu.
2. Right-click the "Hot Spot" box and accept the alert.